Arthur E. Nelson, as Administrator with the Will Annexed of Peter J. T. Nelson, Deceased, Respondent, v. Annie Bohlin, Appellant, et al., Defendants.

In an action to set aside certain transfers of personal property, judgment, insofar as appealed from, unanimously affirmed, with costs. No opinion. Present — Lewis, P. J., Carswell, Adel, Sneed and Wenzel, JJ. [See post, p. 868.]
